<p><em>Note: Okay, I just got the results back from Dr. Blossom and she tells me that this should eventually reverse. Either that or Markham dies, but she assures me that the chances of that are slim. I trust her professional opinion, but keep an eye out for decapitated corpses in the coming weeks, and don't incinerate it without identifying the body. - Veritas</em></p>
