<p><strong>Addendum:</strong> The record has been sealed in anomalous storage and requires level 4 security clearance to access.</p>
<p><strong>Addendum update:</strong> The glasses from the second test have been repaired successfully after 6 hours of work. They will be placed in Senior Researcher Vivic’s office until the glue dries, after which they will be placed within anomalous storage. They have henceforth been dubbed “The Midas Glasses” and will be available to Facility personnel <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">for supervised usage</span> after being cleared by Dr. Veritas or Dr. Hackett.</p>
