<p><strong>Input:</strong> One webcam, 7.25 meters of insulated copper wire<br />
<strong>Setting</strong> Very Fine<br />
<strong>Output:</strong> An ordinary-looking webcam with a very long wire. When plugged into a computer, HD video is automatically recorded onto the hard drive at ████ frames per second. The computer overheated, and the camera was incinerated.</p>
