<hr />
<p><strong>Test 914-1096</strong><br />
<strong>Name:</strong> Dr. Cleveland, D-1080<br />
<strong>Date:</strong> 14/10/2019<br />
<strong>Total items:</strong> One 1:6 model of the <em>JoJo's Bizarre Adventure</em> character Dio Brando, one note reading &quot;Kono Dio Da&quot;, one 2cm by 2cm by 1cm square-shaped neodymium magnet</p>
<p><strong>Input:</strong> Above items<br />
