<p><em>Note: Apart from the obvious, how did it know my fashion choices? More specifically, that was what I was wearing when I arrived at Bratislava as an exchange student. - WR Markham</em></p>
<p><strong>Input:</strong> Above output<br />
<strong>Setting:</strong> Very Fine<br />
